Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-[birds chirping]\N-[theme music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Hilda ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[woman vocalizing]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.83,0:00:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[woffs calling]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.54,0:00:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[Hilda] Look, Mum.\NThe woffs are migrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.63,0:00:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mum] Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.09,0:00:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilda, I've been thinking\Nabout those threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.72,0:00:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm working on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.97,0:01:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but all this trouble\Nhas made me think
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.77,0:01:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,how we're the only people for miles\Nin this whole valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.98,0:01:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's what I love about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.69,0:01:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But wouldn't you like to have\Nsome other kids to talk to?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I have myself to talk to, and Twig.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.82,0:01:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a little trip into Trolberg\Ntomorrow and look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.36,0:01:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mum, no!\N-All I ask is that you keep an open mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.25,0:01:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh, my head is so itchy.\N-Let me check it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.67,0:01:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[meowing]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.83,0:01:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Hilda] Do I have nits?\N-[Mum] Not nits, nittens.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.51,0:01:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-[meowing]\N-[Mum] There. I think that's all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I dug up\Nmy old Pocket Guide to Trolberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take it on the trip tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.47,0:01:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-Okay, how's your head feel?\N-It's not so itchy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Try to get some sleep now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.49,0:02:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.49,0:02:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[ticking]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.68,0:02:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.93,0:02:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[woffs calling]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I need my sketchbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way\NI'm letting you get away this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[calling]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[exhales]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We're moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[footsteps thumping]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[giant] Yes, little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, why do you keep coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you the other night\Njust standing and staring at my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.01,0:03:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm waiting for someone.\N-Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[giant] An old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:04:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time I was here,\Nthere was no house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you sure you have\Nthe exact right place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[giant] I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember the way the horizon looked,\Nthe position of the river...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[inhales deeply]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...the way the air smells.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Some things seem different.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The hills have shifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is the place.\NI remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why haven't they come?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[giant] The details were set\Na very, very long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We would meet here at midnight,\Nbut, uh, perhaps I got the date wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't seem like the kind of person\Nto forget an important date.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ask me, you've been stood up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:05:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see the sense\Nin coming back here night after night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[giant] Something strange has happened,\Nand I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They've all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you're right.\NPerhaps she has, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[yawns] It was nice\Nto meet you properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, how do I get down?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[giant] Climb onto my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[Hilda grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[giant] Thank you for the advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.78,0:06:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-[bell tolling]\N-[horns honking]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now this is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It says here that Trolberg was built
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,right smack in the middle of land\Nthat belonged to trolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they built this wall,\Nto keep the trolls out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]\NCity people are no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That one's available.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Two bedrooms, parking,\Npets okay, close to playground.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-Sounds perfect.\N-Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd be trapped in a house sandwich.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:06:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This could be your school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, explore the playground.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, but I'll keep a low profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[bell tolling]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Where's everybody going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-Inside. Break's over.\N-What's break?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A waste of time if you ask me.\NCome on, David.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that incredibly loud bell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It means time to move it\Nor you'll be late and in trouble again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[David] Yep! Gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Twig, it's good to be home, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[snorting]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum, I'm telling you, those poor\NTrolberg kids live in fear of bells,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,just like trolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilda, it was just a school bell.\NIt's pretty normal, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[Wood Man whistling tune]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, you've let the Wood Man in again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet we wouldn't have neighbors\Nlike this in Trolberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly my point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.73,0:08:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Civilized neighbors don't walk\Ninto your house without asking first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-But he's like part of our family.\N-[Wood Man] No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-Can I have this when you move?\N-We're not moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long day.\NLet's get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen a giant\Nas big as a mountain roaming the valley?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't come here\Nfor the conversation, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[whistling tune]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! You didn't answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts] Slow down!\NI really need to ask you some questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, there's this huge giant\Nwho keeps showing up,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't want to bother Mum about it,\Nfor obvious reasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:08:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but I bet you could help me figure out\Nwhat's going on with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You can pretend not to hear me\Nall you want, but I know you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] Come on, I know you know\Na thing or two about giants.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[Twig grunts, whines]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[Wood Man] Oh, it's still you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you reading\Na book on giants the other night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-You're very observant.\N-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unnerving. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-Would you like some tea?\N-No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That looks like soily water\Nwith sticks in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-[mellow music playing]\N-Why so interested in giants?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I met one last night, a huge one,\Ntaller than the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[Wood Man] Giants that big haven't walked\Nthe earth for an impossibly long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the book you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[Hilda] "The Giants of Old."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[Wood Man] These giants were\Nthe first things to live in these valleys
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,long before people or guys like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles] But most people\Nhave forgotten--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's my one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,According to this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"it was crucial that one giant\Nmust, at all times, be sat atop
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the tallest mountain,\Na long-forgotten peak in the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There, he or she\Nwould gaze tirelessly into the black,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,guarding the earth from anything\Nthat might threaten from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Any young giant\Ncould be summoned as guardian,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,a duty that could last for millennia."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Legend says that the last guardian\Nto serve was this fellow: Jorgen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But where did all the other giants go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.92,0:10:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see,\Neverything started to get smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,People appeared and built towns.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Giants would accidentally step on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There were arguments, fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It just wasn't their world anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So they had to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But where did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-[jazz music playing]\N-No one knows where they went.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Some say they all just jumped as high\Nas they could and drifted off into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.92,0:11:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, my giant's been guarding\Nthe entire planet all on his own
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,for thousands of years,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and no one told him\Nthat everyone else was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.05,0:11:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,His friend was meant to meet him,\Nbut she's gone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor guy.\NHe's all on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[Wood Man] The world became\Ntoo small for his kind to live in anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[sipping]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, how are\Nyour negotiations going with the elves?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the only one\Nwho observes things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Alfur has promised to take me\Nto meet the king tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, barging in on your neighbors\Nis your new thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[sipping]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[birds chirping]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[whining]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, boy.\NYou're on guard duty till I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wish me luck with the king.\N-[whining]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Alfur, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd suggest dressing a little warmer,\Nconsidering our destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[shivering]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.84,0:12:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] How much further\Ndo you think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, 1,500 elf miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[woffs calling]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Hilda, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong way! Wrong way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[Alfur] Whoa!\N[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.71,0:13:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[Hilda] Whoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Woffs are unpredictable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They migrate willy-nilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Alfur.\NJust let me know when you spot the--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, he's trying to shake me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is why one should never fly\Nwithout a permit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[Hilda screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Alfur, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-[gasps] His Majesty!\N-The king!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! The giant girl,\Nsworn enemy of me and my people!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not the enemy, I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, this is Hilda,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and she would so appreciate\Na moment of your royal time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering, stammering]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm busy, busy, busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My royal hands are full!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[echoing] You don't even have hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[rumbling]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.86,0:14:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[thudding]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:14:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilda, I don't think we have time to--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[Hilda] There's a warmth\Ncoming from inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[echoing] Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[rumbling]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[female voice] Hello. Who's there?\NReveal yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You sound like you're just a voice\Nin my head, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.04,0:15:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-No, I'm...\N-[rumbling]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming, grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[birds cawing]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Oof!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! [screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How long have I been asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The, the mountain is a giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me,\Nare you looking for Jorgen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Jorgen? Have you seen him?\NAm I too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've waited for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been coming here for days.\NWhy didn't you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I told him not to wait any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The snow must have blocked my ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.58,0:16:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[all screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Alfur] Oof!\N-[Jorgen] Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:16:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Jorgen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.19,0:17:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[Jorgen] You're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But how?\NWhere were you on the nights I waited?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My love,\Nthings got complicated after you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The little people came.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was fed up\Nand decided to leave or hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't bear to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to the spot we arranged to meet\Nnot long after you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I sat down and waited...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and waited.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I must have fallen asleep at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[birds chirping]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.76,0:17:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[Jorgen] You waited for me\Nfor 4,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.07,0:17:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[Jorgen] Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[elf king] Oh, um, young lady!\N[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem, young lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Young miss, in light of, um,\Nrecent events, I, the king,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.29,0:18:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,would like to declare the conflict\Nbetween yourself and my people over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You've shown yourself to be\Nhonorable and a proponent of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I will speak\Nto the prime minister immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and inform him of the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's not official until you sign.\N-Oh, I'm signing it this minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.98,0:18:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[elves cheering]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's official!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no longer an enemy of my people!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[squeals] There's nothing for Mum\Nto worry about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] What on Earth is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this might seem weird,\Nbut I'm holding a castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and this is the king,\Nand, basically, we don't have to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:18:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The house! Everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone, it's all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't even noticed\Nwhat they've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be all right, Mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:19:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[Wood Man] For the fire\Nin your new place in Trolberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:19:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-I found this in the rubble.\N-My sketchbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I certainly have no use for it.\NIt smells like troll spit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[Hilda sighs]\NI wish I didn't have to leave here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to miss all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.59,0:20:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll even miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You know where to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's very comforting.\N-For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilda, I'm afraid we need to get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[Alfur panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilda! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Alfur!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] I've been up all night filling out\Nthe required paperwork for travel,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's official!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.44,0:20:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"Northern Elven Counties Passport\Nand Permission to Travel."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the first elf from these parts\Nto visit Trolberg
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and file reports on life in the big city!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And, if it's\Nnot too terribly inconvenient,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.79,0:20:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to hitch a ride with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:20:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.21,0:21:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be so nice\Nto have a friend from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hop aboard, Alfur.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.72,0:21:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilda, who are you talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.89,0:21:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I'll tell you on the drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.93,0:21:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-[engine starts]\N-♪ Your name is a triangle ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Your heart is a square ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.15,0:21:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ I love to see you ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Way over there ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Once I was happy ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ You found it intriguing ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[bell tolling]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.54,0:21:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Then you got to me ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Left me waiting ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ You make me feel like a fool ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Waiting for you ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.89,0:21:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you already writing your first report?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.56,0:21:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-We just got here.\N-Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.48,0:22:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to set down my first impressions\Nwhile they're still fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.28,0:22:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,More humans\Nthan I've ever seen in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.90,0:22:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Fascinating noises,\Nand it's all very strange,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.53,0:22:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but also exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.70,0:22:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it just seems loud and crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.75,0:22:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You can barely see the sky,\Nthe trees are too small for climbing,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.46,0:22:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and they built a wall\Nto keep out anything interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.92,0:22:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.35,0:22:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[thunder rumbling]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.31,0:22:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music playing]
